Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount posteo
Host posteo.de
Port 993
User tonipeter@posteo.de
PassCmd "cat ~/resource/keys/pw/posteo"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore posteo-remote
Account posteo

MaildirStore posteo-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/posteo/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/posteo/inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel posteo-inbox
Far :posteo-remote:INBOX
Near :posteo-local:inbox
Create Near

Channel posteo-drafts
Far :posteo-remote:Drafts
Near :posteo-local:drafts
Create Near

Channel posteo-sent
Far :posteo-remote:Sent
Near :posteo-local:sent
Create Near

Channel posteo-deleted
Far :posteo-remote:"Trash"
Near :posteo-local:deleted
Create Near

Channel posteo-archive
Far :posteo-remote:Archive
Near :posteo-local:archive
Create Near

IMAPAccount mailbox
Host imap.mailbox.org
Port 993
User toni.peter@greenbone.net
PassCmd "/home/toni/projects/config/scripts/getMailboxPw.sh"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore mailbox-remote
Account mailbox

MaildirStore mailbox-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/mailbox/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/mailbox/inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel mailbox-inbox
Far :mailbox-remote:INBOX
Near :mailbox-local:inbox
Create Near

Channel mailbox-drafts
Far :mailbox-remote:Drafts
Near :mailbox-local:drafts
Create Near

Channel mailbox-sent
Far :mailbox-remote:Sent
Near :mailbox-local:sent
Create Near

Channel mailbox-deleted
Far :mailbox-remote:Trash
Near :mailbox-local:deleted
Create Near

Channel mailbox-archive
Far :mailbox-remote:Archives
Near :mailbox-local:archive
Create Near

Channel mailbox-archives
Far :mailbox-remote:Archives
Near :mailbox-local:archive
Patterns *
Create Near

Channel mailbox-spam
Far :mailbox-remote:Junk
Near :mailbox-local:spam
Create Near

Group all
Channels posteo-inbox posteo-drafts posteo-sent posteo-deleted posteo-archive mailbox-inbox mailbox-drafts mailbox-sent mailbox-deleted mailbox-archive mailbox-archives mailbox-spam
